Package: justice.gov
Title: API Client for justice.gov Open Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for U.S. Department of Justice open data.
    Access IT leadership directories, governance boards, cost savings data,
    bankruptcy language assistance program data, Chapter 7 trustee reports,
    and USTP enforcement activity files. All functions return tibbles.
